summary: Closest that i can get for her looks.
descriptionHtml:
she is Lvl 2 and race is YgNord(tried an elf race but no change, she got fake elven ears equipped) at riverwood. Got mage stone active and went with imperials. This is closest that i can get to make her look a like, so dont judge me hard:;DD She needs better hair i think. Some of screens taken with shapshooters ENB and some without it.

Mods that you need to get her working:

	
Enhanced Character Edit :http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12951 (for the race and couple of sliders but you could try it without the sliders. There is a optional file)
And remember get the RaceCompatibility mod if you havent got it allready:)

ApachiiSkyHair: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168 

BFG-better face Gen: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6953

Flans Eyes for Skyrim:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14539 (or just change the eye colour if you using different eye sets)

optional:
Nouserheres Ears:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21459

DreamBurrows Princess of The Woods Retexture: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23626 (take the original mod also)

Not sure if needed for eyebrows: 
Better Females by Bella: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812
(load main file then the makeup version 1.)

Use any bodymod you like.
Got Dawnguard installed if that matters.

That\'s all i think. Let me know if missing something again-.-
author: Peterpunk
